{id:"api-2014-spells-wall-of-thorns",name:"Wall of Thorns",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Wall of Thorns"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Level",content:"6"},{title:"Casting Time",content:"1 action"},{title:"Range",content:"120 feet (60ft line)"},{title:"Components",content:"V, S, M"},{title:"Duration",content:"Up to 10 minutes"},{title:"School",content:"Conjuration"},{title:"Save",content:"DEX Save"},{title:"Damage",content:"Piercing"}]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"Effect"},{id:"MultiText",content:["You create a wall of tough, pliable, tangled brush bristling with needle-sharp thorns. The wall appears within range on a solid surface and lasts for the duration. You choose to make the wall up to 60 feet long, 10 feet high, and 5 feet thick or a circle that has a 20-foot diameter and is up to 20 feet high and 5 feet thick. The wall blocks line of sight.","When the wall appears, each creature within its area must make a dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 7d8 piercing damage, or half as much damage on a successful save.","A creature can move through the wall, albeit slowly and painfully. For every 1 foot a creature moves through the wall, it must spend 4 feet of movement. Furthermore, the first time a creature enters the wall on a turn or ends its turn there, the creature must make a dexterity saving throw. It takes 7d8 slashing damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one."]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"At higher levels"},{id:"MultiText",content:["When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, both types of damage increase by 1d8 for each slot level above 6th."]},{id:"Table",content:[["slot level","6","7","8","9"],["damage","7d8","8d8","9d8","10d8"]]}]}